data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous home located in Fishers Cove. This stunning home offers five bedrooms, four and half bathrooms, and two spacious lofts, encompassing 3,989 square feet of pure luxury. The bright open floor plan showcases a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops and a stylish island. With ample storage, a two-car garage, and a private backyard featuring wooded views and a full fence. This home is an impeccable blend of elegance and practicality. Nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac within a desirable neighborhood with low HOA, this gem awaits your exploration. Schedule a tour today to experience the tranquility and sophistication of this Fishers Cove masterpiece. Contact me today to make this dream home yours. *Sellers are offering a 10k credit towards buyers discretion *Home has an Assumable VA loan at 2.25% interest rate*
